de.mnl.osgi.jul2osgi.lib

Class LogManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.logging.LogManager
      • de.mnl.osgi.jul2osgi.lib.LogManager

  • public class LogManager
extends LogManager
    An implementation of LogManager. The system property java.util.logging.manager must be set to de.mnl.osgi.jul2osgi.LogManager in order for this manager to be used. The library that provides this implementation must be on the system classpath (e.g. using bnd's -runpath instruction.
